race.comment: EDITING (3) lightly raced mare adept in all going. Should get the right tempo after retuning with the one trial when a plugging fifth over 1200m at Warwick Farm. Assess on her good fifth in the G3 Fred Best at Doomben last June. RUBI'S SERVE (5) held in high regard by the stable and unwanted in betting on her return, when a slick winner over 1250m at Randwick Kensington. Big weight drop with the claim and no shock to see her finish over the top of these again. JELLICIOUS (4) undefeated in three runs this prep and she looks up to this grade after finishing a respectable fifth to Aeliana over 1400m in the G3 Reginald Allen last year. Will go back from the draw and charge late. RAPBIDASH (7) taken back early from the outside gate when dismal last over 1400m at Warwick Farm. Since fitted with a 900m trial placing at Rosehill. Assess on the good win two-back over this trip at Rosehill. No shock to see go close. TRANSCEND (8) handy NZ filly making her Australian debut. Market best guide.
